2292
01:14:13,726 --> 01:14:14,985
Next, with the silver pomfret,

2293
01:14:14,986 --> 01:14:18,026
it's usually eaten braised in the Korean style in Mokpo.

2294
01:14:18,196 --> 01:14:19,965
So this time, I will braise it with...

2295
01:14:19,966 --> 01:14:22,125
the super sweet soy sauce which Sam loves.

2296
01:14:22,126 --> 01:14:24,136
(Soy sauce braised silver pomfret with radish)

2297
01:14:24,196 --> 01:14:27,766
Lastly, we acquired the aralia sprouts and shrimp.

2298
01:14:27,806 --> 01:14:30,436
I will make the Japanese tempura with them.

2299
01:14:31,206 --> 01:14:33,576
So two dishes are fried.

2300
01:14:33,846 --> 01:14:35,145
- Two dishes are fried.
- One is braised.

2301
01:14:35,146 --> 01:14:37,045
As for our team,

2302
01:14:37,046 --> 01:14:41,086
