2303
01:14:41,116 --> 01:14:42,915
It must be spicy, sweet, and crispy

2304
01:14:42,916 --> 01:14:44,716
- Ho Young Keu Keu - Young Keu Keu

2305
01:14:45,616 --> 01:14:48,026
(Ho Young shows off his Gen MZ charms.)

2306
01:14:48,326 --> 01:14:49,896
- Ho Young Keu Keu - Young Keu Keu

2307
01:14:50,296 --> 01:14:51,725
It's Ho Young Keu Keu.

2308
01:14:51,726 --> 01:14:53,325
(He's indeed a dance machine.)

2309
01:14:53,326 --> 01:14:54,625
- They're good.
- Ho Young Keu Keu

2310
01:14:54,626 --> 01:14:56,335
Actually,

2311
01:14:56,336 --> 01:14:58,595
- I knew it.
- today's cooking showdown...

2312
01:14:58,596 --> 01:15:00,565
- It's a relay.
- has a very special rule.

2313
01:15:00,566 --> 01:15:01,805
- I knew it.
- I knew it.

2314
01:15:01,806 --> 01:15:03,435
It can't be a relay, can it?

2315
01:15:03,436 --> 01:15:06,645
The cooking won't be done by the whole team at once.

2316
01:15:06,646 --> 01:15:07,806
I knew it.

2317
01:15:08,106 --> 01:15:09,815
- Five minutes will be given...
- I knew it.

2318
01:15:09,816 --> 01:15:11,115
To each person as a relay.

2319
01:15:11,116 --> 01:15:12,745
My prediction was exactly right.

2320
01:15:12,746 --> 01:15:14,246
- Exactly as expected.
- I'm doomed.

2321
01:15:15,186 --> 01:15:16,916
I'm most worried about myself.

2322
01:15:17,556 --> 01:15:18,992
I'm in charge of washing the dishes.

2323
01:15:19,016 --> 01:15:21,355
I don't get involved with the cooking at all.

2324
01:15:21,356 --> 01:15:23,096
I get told I get in the way...

2325
01:15:23,196 --> 01:15:24,556
when I try to get involved.

2326
01:15:24,996 --> 01:15:27,365
For the first five minutes,

2327
01:15:27,366 --> 01:15:28,966
the whole team can work together.

2328
01:15:29,496 --> 01:15:31,135
That much is fine.

2329
01:15:31,136 --> 01:15:35,036
After that, it will be the member, member, member, and chef.

2330
01:15:35,166 --> 01:15:37,035
Member, member, member, and chef.

2331
01:15:37,036 --> 01:15:38,405
The dish should be ready after that.

2332
01:15:38,406 --> 01:15:40,145
- It's better for us then.
- What about us?

2333
01:15:40,146 --> 01:15:41,605
- Member, member, and chef.
- My turn...

2334
01:15:41,606 --> 01:15:43,416
- will come quickly.
- As for this team,

2335
01:15:43,516 --> 01:15:47,385
it will be member 1, member 2, member 1, and chef.

2336
01:15:47,386 --> 01:15:49,955
Member 2, member 1, member 2, and chef.

2337
01:15:49,956 --> 01:15:51,085
- That's nice.
- No!

2338
01:15:51,086 --> 01:15:53,055
- But Se Yoon is great at cooking.
- That makes it fair.

2339
01:15:53,056 --> 01:15:54,725
But it's crucial that Jong Min will go twice.

2340
01:15:54,726 --> 01:15:55,755
- Right.
- That's crucial.

2341
01:15:55,756 --> 01:15:57,795
I don't know how to cook at all!

2342
01:15:57,796 --> 01:15:58,995
(He's actually a useless card.)

2343
01:15:58,996 --> 01:16:00,095
- The last five minutes...
- All right.

2344
01:16:00,096 --> 01:16:01,125
I don't know how to cook at all.

2345
01:16:01,126 --> 01:16:03,695
For the last cooking session of the chefs,

2346
01:16:03,696 --> 01:16:05,466
it will be ten minutes.

2347
01:16:05,936 --> 01:16:08,965
The mess we made must be sorted out in ten minutes.

2348
01:16:08,966 --> 01:16:11,876
This means the order of the members will be important.

2349
01:16:12,236 --> 01:16:14,275
- All right. Here it is.
- It's a draw for the order?

2350
01:16:14,276 --> 01:16:15,476
This is for the team of three.

2351
01:16:15,576 --> 01:16:17,776
Show us all of your draws.

2352
01:16:18,476 --> 01:16:20,145
One, two, three.

2353
01:16:20,146 --> 01:16:22,715
- Number 1.
- Se Yoon 1, Jong Min 2.

2354
01:16:22,716 --> 01:16:25,515
(Team Sam Kim cooking order)

2355
01:16:25,516 --> 01:16:28,056
(All members will cook together first.)

2356
01:16:28,226 --> 01:16:30,895
That's a relief. Jong Min must do everything at the end.

2357
01:16:30,896 --> 01:16:32,055
Right.

2358
01:16:32,056 --> 01:16:33,566
I can't go last.

2359
01:16:33,666 --> 01:16:35,096
I should've drawn number one.

2360
01:16:35,496 --> 01:16:38,895
DinDin 1, Joon 2, Seon Ho 3.

2361
01:16:38,896 --> 01:16:41,166
(Team Ho Young cooking order)

2362
01:16:41,306 --> 01:16:44,035
I can tell you what to do when we work together.

2363
01:16:44,036 --> 01:16:45,405
(How will the wild cooking battle go with the chefs' pride on the line?)

2364
01:16:45,406 --> 01:16:48,805
For the first five minutes, all members will work together...

2365
01:16:48,806 --> 01:16:50,476
- on the ingredients.
- Right.

2366
01:16:50,916 --> 01:16:53,115
- Let's go!
- Gosh!

2367
01:16:53,116 --> 01:16:54,316
- Let's go!
- Gosh!

2368
01:16:54,616 --> 01:16:56,586
- Stay calm!
- Stay calm!

2369
01:16:57,986 --> 01:16:59,826
(Making a fuss)

2370
01:17:00,086 --> 01:17:01,825
(Joon: Vegetable preparation, Seon Ho: Octopus preparation)

2371
01:17:01,826 --> 01:17:03,395
(DinDin: Shrimp preparation, Ho Young: Everything else)

2372
01:17:03,396 --> 01:17:05,155
Where are they? I'll wash them.

2373
01:17:05,156 --> 01:17:06,642
(Seon Ho works on the webfoot octopus right away.)

2374
01:17:06,666 --> 01:17:07,995
Stay calm, Seon Ho.

2375
01:17:07,996 --> 01:17:09,542
(The webfoot octopus legs are separated.)

2376
01:17:09,566 --> 01:17:12,295
I've cooked the webfoot octopus at home often...

2377
01:17:12,296 --> 01:17:14,405
