2550
01:23:13,726 --> 01:23:16,066
(You're doing well!)

2551
01:23:16,236 --> 01:23:17,236
(Panting)

2552
01:23:17,237 --> 01:23:18,266
Gosh.

2553
01:23:19,166 --> 01:23:21,536
- Hurry up, Se Yoon!
- Who suggested sujebi?

2554
01:23:21,866 --> 01:23:23,006
Gosh!

2555
01:23:23,306 --> 01:23:24,775
- What should I do next?
- Don't you need more water?

2556
01:23:24,776 --> 01:23:26,245
Check the Manila clams.

2557
01:23:26,246 --> 01:23:27,345
The Manila clams are in water.

2558
01:23:27,346 --> 01:23:28,475
- Taste it.
- They're not open yet.

2559
01:23:28,476 --> 01:23:29,545
- He tells you to taste it.
- Spoon.

2560
01:23:29,546 --> 01:23:31,045
If it's not open, push it open and try it.

2561
01:23:31,046 --> 01:23:32,046
Where?

2562
01:23:32,676 --> 01:23:35,546
Okay? Try the broth and see if it's salty or not.

2563
