It's salty!

2564
01:23:39,726 --> 01:23:40,786
You can add water now.

2565
01:23:41,026 --> 01:23:43,725
(Adding water to the Manila clam broth)

2566
01:23:43,726 --> 01:23:46,465
- And wash the potatoes.
- Wash the potatoes.

2567
01:23:46,466 --> 01:23:48,696
- Wash them and leave them.
- Wash them and leave them.

2568
01:23:49,296 --> 01:23:51,035
Okay. How many?

2569
01:23:51,036 --> 01:23:52,435
- What are you doing?
- Just two.

2570
01:23:52,436 --> 01:23:53,665
Why are you so slow?

2571
01:23:53,666 --> 01:23:54,766
(Scolding him)

2572
01:23:55,136 --> 01:23:58,436
(Se Yoon is doing a lot of work as the ace player.)

2573
01:23:58,536 --> 01:24:00,005
You have two minutes left.

2574
01:24:00,006 --> 01:24:01,246
Hurry, Se Yoon.

2575
01:24:02,346 --> 01:24:03,876
Don't pester me.

2576
01:24:03,976 --> 01:24:06,645
- The chef will be hurt again.
- Okay.

2577
01:24:06,646 --> 01:24:07,646
- We have to win.
- You heard him.

2578
01:24:07,647 --> 01:24:08,915
- Right. We have to win.
- We have to win.

2579
01:24:08,916 --> 01:24:10,985
His son said, "I think I can beat you."

2580
01:24:10,986 --> 01:24:13,555
Three, two, one.

2581
01:24:13,556 --> 01:24:14,625
Switch.

2582
01:24:14,626 --> 01:24:16,396
- Come here.
- Joon, Jong Min. Switch.

2583
01:24:16,556 --> 01:24:18,426
- Go away.
- Okay. Hurry.

2584
01:24:19,026 --> 01:24:20,166
Switch.

2585
01:24:20,366 --> 01:24:22,696
(Team Ho Young's weak link, Lee Joon steps up.)

2586
01:24:23,236 --> 01:24:24,735
(He cleans the aralia sprouts, which wasn't finished earlier.)

2587
01:24:24,736 --> 01:24:25,996
Scratch the aralia sprouts.

2588
01:24:26,166 --> 01:24:27,435
That's enough.

2589
01:24:27,436 --> 01:24:29,505
- Is this enough? Just like this?
- Yes. It's good enough.

2590
01:24:29,506 --> 01:24:30,676
Okay. It's done.

2591
01:24:30,806 --> 01:24:32,906
Because I'm very weak in this area,

2592
01:24:33,106 --> 01:24:34,246
I feel self-conscious.

2593
01:24:35,206 --> 01:24:40,486
It is my role to do my best so as not to be a burden.

2594
01:24:40,816 --> 01:24:43,115
- I wash them like this.
- Okay.

2595
01:24:43,116 --> 01:24:45,015
It's done. You can take them out now.

2596
01:24:45,016 --> 01:24:46,826
- Take them out.
- And remove the water.

2597
01:24:47,486 --> 01:24:49,255
Squeeze out more water.

2598
01:24:49,256 --> 01:24:50,426
Hurry and put them down!

2599
01:24:50,656 --> 01:24:52,455
- It must be cold.
- Place them there.

2600
01:24:52,456 --> 01:24:53,625
- Put them here.
- What's next?

2601
