2747
01:29:49,026 --> 01:29:50,056
It's like...

2748
01:29:51,296 --> 01:29:53,155
Just like its name, I'll let you...

2749
01:29:53,156 --> 01:29:56,466
enjoy a sweet and pleasurable taste.

2750
01:29:56,836 --> 01:29:59,266
(Pouring generously)

2751
