2755
01:30:09,846 --> 01:30:10,915
(Simmer it for a while, and it's done.)

2756
01:30:10,916 --> 01:30:12,815
I knew it. It's just as expected.

2757
01:30:12,816 --> 01:30:15,015
Someone who has won once is bound to win again.

2758
01:30:15,016 --> 01:30:17,362
