(Lemon butter grilled halibut)

2764
01:30:26,556 --> 01:30:27,895
The magic powder is added.

2765
01:30:27,896 --> 01:30:30,836
(Seasoned only with salt and pepper)

2766
01:30:31,736 --> 01:30:32,736
(Minimizing seasoning for the natural flavor of ingredients)

2767
01:30:32,737 --> 01:30:34,537
- How would he...
- You don't score the fish?

2768
01:30:34,666 --> 01:30:36,236
I should score it.

2769
01:30:36,506 --> 01:30:38,136
- You score it?
- Good.

2770
01:30:38,536 --> 01:30:40,345
There you go. Score the fish!

2771
01:30:40,346 --> 01:30:42,446
Let's go. Even cuts.

2772
01:30:42,606 --> 01:30:44,576
