- It's too low.
- Why is the heat too low?

2777
01:30:54,486 --> 01:30:56,695
- Was it turned off?
- Right. It's okay.

2778
01:30:56,696 --> 01:30:57,902
(The heat is too low because of the wind.)

2779
01:30:57,926 --> 01:31:00,366
(Calm)

2780
01:31:00,496 --> 01:31:01,765
Are you using another burner?

2781
