- Yes.
- He's changing the burner.

2782
01:31:04,036 --> 01:31:06,836
(Replacing it with the burner used for making broth)

2783
01:31:07,166 --> 01:31:08,166
(Will he be able to overcome this crisis?)

2784
01:31:08,167 --> 01:31:09,606
The heat is too low.

2785
