- He's different!

2797
01:31:35,596 --> 01:31:37,996
(They sing the cheering song spontaneously.)

2798
01:31:38,636 --> 01:31:39,665
(Smiling)

2799
01:31:39,666 --> 01:31:41,366
- This is amazing.
- Ho Young Keu Keu

2800
01:31:44,606 --> 01:31:46,946
