I got vinegar in my eye.

2809
01:32:03,156 --> 01:32:06,356
(It splashed into his eye.)

2810
01:32:06,426 --> 01:32:08,165
(Passing the vinegar to him anyway)

2811
01:32:08,166 --> 01:32:09,166
Endure it.

2812
01:32:09,167 --> 01:32:11,072
(Green and red chili peppers, green onions, and vinegar)

2813
01:32:11,096 --> 01:32:12,665
(Soy sauce)

2814
01:32:12,666 --> 01:32:14,135
