2817
01:32:17,706 --> 01:32:20,175
Chef, you're adding more sugar than we expected.

2818
01:32:20,176 --> 01:32:21,805
Don't disturb him.

2819
01:32:21,806 --> 01:32:23,246
- Don't disturb him.
- Okay.

2820
01:32:24,846 --> 01:32:26,215
Chicken stock.

2821
01:32:26,216 --> 01:32:27,846
